Package: linuxmuster-squid
Version: @VERSION@
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Kevin Stenzel <kevin@ks98.de>
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Depends: python3 (>= 3.11), adduser, openssl
Recommends: docker.io | docker-ce
Description: Control plane for containerized linuxmuster-squid proxies
 REST API + CLI to manage per-school Squid proxy containers (Kerberos SSO,
 AD group ACLs, SNI filtering) with digest-pinned, health-checked, auto-rolling
 updates. Ships a self-contained Python virtualenv under /opt/linuxmuster-squid.
